item.title: My Cat Ulee
item.description: Intro too old for retrieving images. we must move forward to todays news! This adorable little monster is my cat Ulee (OO-lee). He’s a rescue cat that I got when I was having a hard time with mental health about 2 years ago here in Norfolk. At the time, I thought that maybe some kind of emotional support animal would be good for my health. Now, some people might say that it’s not a good idea to get an animal when you’re in that kind of place.
